<T>__{on tv:}
<A>__{its a party for kates birthday thrown at the kramers house...same crowd of people as the christmas party, cheesy happy birthday decorations. the image jerks up and down, surveying the crowd... bill kramer at the piano, playing some light cocktail music ...kate talking with a group of friends...}
