<A>__{kate looks at him expectantly. then...}
<C>__{jack }
<P>__{(singing to her)}
<D>__{oh those fingers in my hair, that sly come hither stare, strips my conscience bare, its witchcraft...}
<A>__{jack doesnt have the greatest voice in the world but hes not the least bit self conscious...and kate seems to like it, theres a twinkle in her eye...some of the guests focus their attention on jack and kate. jack winces, embarrassed, as he watches himself sing...}
<C>__{jack }
<D>__{...and ive got no defense for it, that heat is too intense for it, what good would common sense for it do...}
